<headline>Special Weather Statement issued March 13 at 4:28AM MDT  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Rain and snow showers across Southwest MT today...
Rain and snow showers will move across Southwest MT today. A mix
of rain and snow will be possible for elevations below 6000 feet,
with mostly snow falling for elevations above 6000 feet.
New snow accumulations today for elevations above 6000 feet of
1 to 2 inches are possible. Some higher elevation roadways could
be snow covered and slippery, with visibility reduced at times.</description>
